<h2>Who we are</h2>
<p>ARIA Capital Holdings LLC is a Wyoming limited liability company (EIN 42-3423692) focused on financial education and healthcare career resources. We publish practical, research-backed guides on building passive income, navigating the CRNA path, and making sound financial decisions in healthcare careers.</p>

<h2>What this site is</h2>
<p>We publish guides on passive income strategies — including DeFi yield, Amazon KDP, Etsy digital downloads, print-on-demand, affiliate SEO, and options strategies — alongside career resources for ICU nurses pursuing CRNA school and financial independence.</p>
<p>Our goal is straightforward: give healthcare professionals the financial and career information they need to make informed decisions, backed by real data and honest analysis rather than hype.</p>

<h2>Our editorial standards</h2>
<p>We only cover strategies and products that have been evaluated against real-world outcomes. If something doesn't work, we say so. Income projections are illustrative, not guarantees. Nothing on this site is financial advice — always consult a licensed financial advisor before making investment decisions.</p>

<h2>Affiliation and transparency</h2>
<p>Some links on this site are affiliate links — we earn a small commission if you sign up or buy through them, at no extra cost to you. This does not change our rankings or recommendations. See the <a href="affiliate-disclosure.html">full disclosure</a> for details.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
